[{"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "象徵王之名詞　前篇", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "某天，南格拉斯迪亞大陸上空出現了異界的裂縫。並且以此為契機，各地開始傳出關於神秘龍族的傳言。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "在某個平原從魔獸手中拯救了村民。在某座森林將龍族化為了焦炭。在某處山岳悠然地眺望著天空。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然而不管是哪個傳言，其相貌大致上都相同。皆說他的巨大身軀帶著黑色，龐大翅翼有著金色的紋路。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "關於神秘龍族的傳言，很快地擴散開來。不知何時，人們為他取了別稱。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "因其莊嚴氣勢而得名「漆黑之王」。因其吐焰慘狀而得名「恐怖之王」。因其難以接近之強大而得名「孤高之王」。人們用各自不同的別稱稱呼著神秘龍族。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "擁有複數之名，也就證明人們對神秘龍族懷有各自不同的印象。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "沒錯，這個時候還是如此……", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 210122011, "title": "象徵王之名詞　前篇 (210122011)"}, {"conversations": [{"audioPaths": [], "content": "象徵王之名詞　後篇", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "由異界的裂縫出現的神秘龍族，受到人們用各式各樣的別稱來稱呼。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "然而，不知何時，眾多名稱逐漸集中至一個名字。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "支撐巨大身軀的漆黑雙翼，燒卻一切的紅蓮吐息，王者之證的崇高傲骨。──故稱「黑炎王」。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "神奇的是，那個別稱，正與來自異界的人們對他的稱呼相同。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "「黑炎王」身為王中之王，對侵犯自己領域者，皆平等地待以猛烈制裁。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "展現其威嚴之名之所以會集中至一個名稱，是由於以其他名字呼喚者全被他化為了灰燼。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "王所通過的道路，平原、森林與山丘都將化為焦土。侵略王之領域者，人類、野獸與龍族都將化為焦炭。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}, {"audioPaths": [], "content": "任何人都無法接近，今日的他也單純地作為王中之王而存在。", "isSys": false, "speakerIcon": null, "speakerName": "", "type": "conversation"}], "id": 210122012, "title": "象徵王之名詞　後篇 (210122012)"}]